<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>عَنْ عَائِشَةَ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>قَالَه عَبدَة، عَنْ هِشام، عَنْ عُروة.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>أُراه أبا عُثمان المَدَنِيّ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>